flowchart TD
    App[Application] --> Router{Shard Router}
    Router --> HashFn[Hash shard key]
    HashFn --> ShardID{Shard ID?}
    ShardID -->|0| Shard0[(Shard 0\nUsers 0-999k)]
    ShardID -->|1| Shard1[(Shard 1\nUsers 1M-1.9M)]
    ShardID -->|2| Shard2[(Shard 2\nUsers 2M-2.9M)]
    ShardID -->|3| Shard3[(Shard 3\nUsers 3M+)]
    Shard0 --> Result[Query Result]
    Shard1 --> Result
    Shard2 --> Result
    Shard3 --> Result
    Result --> App
